---
title: Chicken, Coconut and Lentil Soup with Baby Spinach and Buttery Naans
description: Layers of flavour from warming pasanda spices, garlic, vegetables and coconut milk make this a comforting and nourishing soup that's perfect for autumn. Scoop up the lentils with the naan or dip it in your soup!
